data.description: Price Improvement! This home is a great value in this wonderful community! Welcome to your dream home in the prestigious gated community of Castlebrook Crossing! This immaculate residence offers the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and versatility. With 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a versatile upstairs bonus room that could easily serve as a 5th bedroom, this home provides ample space for your family's needs. Step inside to discover an open and spacious floor plan designed for modern living. The main level boasts a well-appointed kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and the adjacent dining area and family room create a welcoming space for gatherings and relaxation. The primary bedroom suite is a peaceful haven featuring a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom with dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. It's the ideal place to unwind after a long day. The home even features a whole home generator so you won't lose power and a BRAND NEW ROOF! Castlebrook Crossing is a gated community, offering peace of mind and an added layer of security for you and your family. This home is conveniently located near top-rated schools, shopping, dining, and recreational opportunities. It's also a short drive from major highways, making your daily commute a breeze. Residents of Castlebrook Crossing enjoy access to a variety of amenities, including a community pool, playgrounds, fishing ponds, and a basketball court. Come see this home today!
